Connection Model:
C: COMMAND ARGS
S: +OK <PROCESS ID>
S: +<PROCESS ID> <RESPONSE>
S: +DONE <PROCESS ID>

COMMAND:
<command number> <args...>

* Command Number:
LXNM_VERSION                   0
LXNM_DEVICE_STATUS             1
LXNM_DEVICE_INFORMATION        2
LXNM_ETHERNET_UP               3
LXNM_ETHERNET_DOWN             4
LXNM_ETHERNET_REPAIR           5
LXNM_WIRELESS_UP               6
LXNM_WIRELESS_DOWN             7
LXNM_WIRELESS_REPAIR           8
LXNM_WIRELESS_CONNECT          9
LXNM_WIRELESS_SCAN             10

* LXNM_DEVICE_STATUS
[Command Number] <interface>

	Return Data Structure:
	<interface> <status number> <content>

	Status Number:
	LXNM_STATUS_MESSAGE			0
	LXNM_STATUS_NETDEV_CONNECTING		1
	LXNM_STATUS_NETDEV_CONNECTED 		2
	LXNM_STATUS_NETDEV_DISCONNECTED 	3
	LXNM_STATUS_NETDEV_PROBLEM		4
	LXNM_STATUS_NETDEV_BOTHRS		5
	LXNM_STATUS_NETDEV_SENDDATA		6
	LXNM_STATUS_NETDEV_RECVDATA		7
	LXNM_STATUS_NETDEV_WIRELESS_QUALITY	8

* LXNM_DEVICE_INFORMATION
[Command Number] <interface> <flags>

	flags:
	LXNM_FLAGS_DEVICE_INFO_STATUS		(1<<0)
	LXNM_FLAGS_DEVICE_INFO_TYPE		(1<<1)
	LXNM_FLAGS_DEVICE_INFO_MAC		(1<<2)
	LXNM_FLAGS_DEVICE_INFO_IPADDR		(1<<3)
	LXNM_FLAGS_DEVICE_INFO_BROADCAST	(1<<4)
	LXNM_FLAGS_DEVICE_INFO_NETMASK		(1<<5)
	LXNM_FLAGS_DEVICE_INFO_GATEWAY		(1<<6)
	LXNM_FLAGS_DEVICE_INFO_DESTINATION	(1<<7)
	LXNM_FLAGS_DEVICE_INFO_QUALITY		(1<<8)

	Return Data Structure:
	[Length (1 Byte)][Content][...]

	LXNM_FLAGS_DEVICE_INFO_STATUS Will Return:
		LXNM_STATUS_NETDEV_CONNECTING		1
		LXNM_STATUS_NETDEV_CONNECTED 		2
		LXNM_STATUS_NETDEV_DISCONNECTED 	3
		LXNM_STATUS_NETDEV_PROBLEM		4

	LXNM_FLAGS_DEVICE_INFO_TYPE Will Return:
		LXNM_CONNECTION_TYPE_ETHERNET    0
		LXNM_CONNECTION_TYPE_WIRELESS    1
		LXNM_CONNECTION_TYPE_PPP         2

* LXNM_WIRELESS_UP:
[Command Number] <interface>

* LXNM_WIRELESS_DOWN:
[Command Number] <interface>

* LXNM_WIRELESS_REPAIR:
[Command Number] <interface>

* LXNM_WIRELESS_CONNECT:
[Command Number] <interface> <essid> <apaddr> <key> <protocol> <key_mgmt> <grpup> <pairwise>

* LXNM_WIRELESS_SCAN:
[Command Number] <interface>

	Return Data Structure:
	<essid> <apaddr> <quality> <protocol> <key_mgmt> <grpup> <pairwise>\n
